headline: Diamondback Energy price target raised to $180 from $164 at Roth Capital
summary: Roth Capital raised the firm’s price target on Diamondback Energy (FANG) to $180 from $164 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares following the company’s Q4 report and Q1 production guidance.
